00:25:05,640 --> 00:25:06,760
Not at all.

591
00:25:06,760 --> 00:25:08,380
What about my answer. Are you satisfied?

592
00:25:08,880 --> 00:25:09,520
Yeah.

593
00:25:09,520 --> 00:25:10,560
Completely satisfied.

594
00:25:10,560 --> 00:25:11,680
Because the answer I wanted

595
00:25:11,680 --> 00:25:12,470
is exactly that one.

596
00:25:12,470 --> 00:25:13,350
You're good-looking.

597
00:25:13,350 --> 00:25:15,350
How could it be that
no one's reached out to you?

598
00:25:16,070 --> 00:25:18,470
Well, it's not just about looks though.

599
00:25:18,470 --> 00:25:19,160
Let me hear it.

600
00:25:19,160 --> 00:25:20,040
What did you say?

601
00:25:20,350 --> 00:25:20,950
Well done.

602
00:25:21,800 --> 00:25:23,160
You made it through the test.

603
00:25:25,190 --> 00:25:26,680
Let's grab a drink.

604
00:25:26,680 --> 00:25:27,350
Have another one.

605
00:25:27,350 --> 00:25:28,190
Let's go.

606
00:25:30,520 --> 00:25:31,280
What?

607
00:25:31,280 --> 00:25:32,100
What are you humming?

608
00:25:34,160 --> 00:25:35,110
Some people...

609
00:25:36,880 --> 00:25:39,110
Honestly, I don't care about the results.

610
00:25:39,110 --> 00:25:40,350
Because I think

611
00:25:40,350 --> 00:25:41,760
there's no need to rely on it

612
00:25:41,760 --> 00:25:43,430
to judge what we have between us.

613
00:25:43,430 --> 00:25:45,230
If I can't get it over,

614
00:25:45,230 --> 00:25:46,710
I'd just drain myself emotionally.

615
00:25:47,520 --> 00:25:48,110
If

616
00:25:48,110 --> 00:25:49,710
Lu comes and asks you,

617
00:25:49,710 --> 00:25:50,640
what would you say?

618
00:25:51,350 --> 00:25:52,760
Like, if he actually shows up

619
00:25:52,760 --> 00:25:54,830
and asks if you'd choose him.

620
00:25:55,110 --> 00:25:55,800
I wouldn't.

621
00:25:55,840 --> 00:25:57,140
His feelings for me are rational.

622
00:25:57,140 --> 00:25:58,000
I wouldn't choose him.

623
00:25:58,920 --> 00:25:59,830
Drop this topic.

624
00:25:59,830 --> 00:26:00,920
Would you tell him directly?

625
00:26:01,880 --> 00:26:03,050
He wouldn't get

626
00:26:03,050 --> 00:26:04,430
a single vote from me tonight.

627
00:26:11,800 --> 00:26:13,760
Attention, islanders.

628
00:26:13,760 --> 00:26:17,160
Here are the rules for tomorrow's date.

629
00:26:18,560 --> 00:26:20,070
There are three invitation cards.

630
00:26:21,400 --> 00:26:23,590
They're hidden somewhere on the island.

631
00:26:24,000 --> 00:26:26,880
You must solve the Puzzle Book
in the mailbox.

632
00:26:26,880 --> 00:26:29,920
It'll reveal where
and when the invitation cards appear.

633
00:26:30,160 --> 00:26:30,470
So...

634
00:26:30,470 --> 00:26:32,190
(The time and location must match)
we

635
00:26:32,190 --> 00:26:33,880
need to know
when and where they show up.

636
00:26:34,070 --> 00:26:35,110
Now?

637
00:26:37,400 --> 00:26:39,470
The first to crack the puzzle

638
00:26:39,470 --> 00:26:40,710
will get the chance to unlock

639
00:26:40,710 --> 00:26:43,470
an romantic luxury date.

640
00:26:47,310 --> 00:26:48,110
Luxury.

641
00:26:48,110 --> 00:26:48,950
Romantic.

642
00:26:48,950 --> 00:26:50,470
Must be something good.

643
00:26:50,470 --> 00:26:51,680
Are you quick to think?

644
00:26:51,830 --> 00:26:52,280
Yeah, I am.

645
00:26:52,280 --> 00:26:53,430
Yeah? Really?

646
00:26:53,430 --> 00:26:54,520
I just talk slow.

647
00:26:55,040 --> 00:26:56,040
Is that so?

648
00:26:59,350 --> 00:27:00,190
Are you smart?

649
00:27:00,190 --> 00:27:00,830
Honestly,

650
00:27:00,830 --> 00:27:01,430
not really.

651
00:27:01,430 --> 00:27:02,230
Well, that's tough.

652
00:27:02,710 --> 00:27:03,520
I'm not smart either.

653
00:27:03,520 --> 00:27:04,430
But I want to

654
00:27:04,430 --> 00:27:06,310
go on a luxury date.

655
00:27:07,280 --> 00:27:08,310
Then I think...

656
00:27:08,310 --> 00:27:09,230
Yang, you...

657
00:27:09,640 --> 00:27:10,830
Let me work my brain

658
00:27:11,350 --> 00:27:13,950
and win my own romantic luxury date.

659
00:27:13,950 --> 00:27:14,680
Right?

660
00:27:14,680 --> 00:27:15,880
I'd definitely think hard too.

661
00:27:16,190 --> 00:27:16,880
Honestly,

662
00:27:16,880 --> 00:27:18,590
I want to go on an off-island date.

663
00:27:18,590 --> 00:27:19,880
This time, it's about reasoning.

664
00:27:19,880 --> 00:27:22,880
No need for physical clashes
or fighting over it.

665
00:27:23,310 --> 00:27:24,950
Feels like there's finally a hope.

666
00:27:26,310 --> 00:27:27,830
Sis, we've got to win this one.

667
00:27:27,830 --> 00:27:29,800
Come on, I'm seriously scared right now.

668
00:27:29,800 --> 00:27:30,920
What should we do?

669
00:27:30,920 --> 00:27:31,640
You don't want it?

670
00:27:31,640 --> 00:27:32,470
I'll go with someone else.

671
00:27:32,470 --> 00:27:33,680
A proper meal is tempting.

672
00:27:33,680 --> 00:27:34,470
Come on, let's go.

673
00:27:35,350 --> 00:27:36,040
I think

674
00:27:36,040 --> 00:27:38,880
Yijia is not interested in any guy here.

675
00:27:38,880 --> 00:27:40,830
And I'm not interested in any girl here.

676
00:27:40,830 --> 00:27:41,640
So...

677
00:27:42,470 --> 00:27:43,520
we can team up for now.

678
00:27:43,800 --> 00:27:44,990
(Caring for family)
Let's hang out.

679
00:27:45,110 --> 00:27:47,280
Gotta make my sister's wish come true.

680
00:27:47,880 --> 00:27:48,800
Let's take it out.

681
00:27:49,710 --> 00:27:50,560
Come on.

682
00:27:51,280 --> 00:27:52,160
They're different.

683
00:27:52,160 --> 00:27:52,560
Here.

684
00:27:52,560 --> 00:27:54,000
Three copies of the Puzzle Books.

685
00:27:54,520 --> 00:27:55,430
This one's a hint.

686
00:27:55,710 --> 00:27:56,920
The hint is "Couple".

687
00:27:57,340 --> 00:28:00,620
(Puzzle Book 1. Hint: Couple)

688
00:28:00,640 --> 00:28:01,800
Why are there two of them?

689
00:28:13,100 --> 00:28:14,220
(Puzzle Book 2)

690
00:28:14,220 --> 00:28:15,430
What is this drawing?

691
00:28:15,430 --> 00:28:16,590
I don't get what this means.

692
00:28:18,830 --> 00:28:20,110
Qiong.

693
00:28:20,470 --> 00:28:22,880
You're the most confident person
in my heart.

694
00:28:23,520 --> 00:28:25,190
(Puzzle Book 3)
My world, ruled by you.

695
00:28:25,190 --> 00:28:26,800
At the card table of life,

696
00:28:26,800 --> 00:28:27,900
I wandered without direction

697
00:28:28,190 --> 00:28:30,000
until you showed up
as that decisive King

698
00:28:30,000 --> 00:28:31,000
and changed everything.

699
00:28:37,520 --> 00:28:38,760
I'm bad with numbers.

700
00:28:40,350 --> 00:28:41,680
Can you make sense of this?

701
00:28:41,830 --> 00:28:42,520
Yeah.

702
00:28:42,520 --> 00:28:43,350
I think,

703
00:28:43,350 --> 00:28:44,040
for example,

704
00:28:44,040 --> 00:28:45,710
letters like A, D, K

705
00:28:45,710 --> 00:28:46,950
must have some special meaning.

706
00:28:46,950 --> 00:28:48,280
Could be about time and place.

707
00:28:48,470 --> 00:28:49,310
Numbers aside,

708
00:28:49,310 --> 00:28:50,170
A, D, K are pointing

709
00:28:50,170 --> 00:28:51,000
to something else.

710
00:28:52,000 --> 00:28:53,230
What are we looking for?

711
00:28:53,230 --> 00:28:55,160
You've got to deduce it
before you search.

712
00:28:55,160 --> 00:28:56,070
Come on.

713
00:28:56,400 --> 00:28:58,110
It's about time and place, right?

714
00:28:58,110 --> 00:28:58,680
Yeah.

715
00:28:58,680 --> 00:28:59,230
Exactly.

716
00:28:59,230 --> 00:29:02,040
We just need to work out
the time and location.

717
00:29:02,400 --> 00:29:04,280
I think all the numbers,

718
00:29:04,280 --> 00:29:05,190
like nine seats,

719
00:29:05,190 --> 00:29:06,680
June, and four seasons,

720
00:29:07,350 --> 00:29:09,350
could point to a time.

721
00:29:09,350 --> 00:29:12,040
(Yang Tianyu: the numbers point to a time)
And this is a place.

722
00:29:12,040 --> 00:29:13,040
I mean ADK.

723
00:29:13,040 --> 00:29:14,340
(The letters point to a location)

724
00:29:14,340 --> 00:29:16,190
I have no idea what these mean.

725
00:29:22,520 --> 00:29:24,190
What does 996 even mean?

726
00:29:34,590 --> 00:29:35,920
Time and place.

727
00:29:38,070 --> 00:29:39,110
What on earth is this?

728
00:29:39,110 --> 00:29:39,880
And what are these?

729
00:29:41,190 --> 00:29:42,000
No clue at all.

730
00:29:42,000 --> 00:29:43,340
(Mind's stuck)

731
00:29:43,520 --> 00:29:44,380
Can't figure it out.

732
00:29:44,380 --> 00:29:46,040
Totally clueless here.

733
00:29:47,520 --> 00:29:49,350
We're just staring
at each other blankly.

734
00:29:49,520 --> 00:29:51,590
We're both acting slow today.

735
00:29:51,800 --> 00:29:53,560
Not a single idea between us.

736
00:29:53,920 --> 00:29:55,400
Can't wrap my head around it.

737
00:29:55,920 --> 00:29:58,110
But honestly, I'm hoping for a date.

738
00:29:58,280 --> 00:30:02,000
I can feel Tianyu getting closer.

739
00:30:02,760 --> 00:30:03,800
So gentle.

740
00:30:04,590 --> 00:30:05,800
The gentle chef.

741
00:30:09,830 --> 00:30:10,800
Han, sit over here.

742
00:30:11,310 --> 00:30:12,000
Why like this?

743
00:30:12,000 --> 00:30:13,880
Your left side looks better on camera.

744
00:30:15,310 --> 00:30:17,710
If we can go out together on a date

745
00:30:17,710 --> 00:30:18,520
and spend more time

746
00:30:18,520 --> 00:30:19,880
to connect,

747
00:30:19,880 --> 00:30:20,800
that's a good thing.

748
00:30:29,190 --> 00:30:30,590
I really want to get the Date Card.

749
00:30:30,590 --> 00:30:32,680
I still want to spend more time
with Tianyu.

750
00:30:38,110 --> 00:30:39,040
Because I feel that

751
00:30:39,040 --> 00:30:40,190
a date can change a person.

752
00:30:43,800 --> 00:30:45,040
And it has already changed him.

753
00:30:45,710 --> 00:30:47,160
If I get the Date Card,

754
00:30:47,160 --> 00:30:48,680
I'll write Tianyu's name on it

755
00:30:49,040 --> 00:30:51,070
and talk about the things
I'm interested in.

756
00:30:51,070 --> 00:30:52,590
Maybe deepen our bond a little.

757
00:30:52,590 --> 00:30:53,800
Get to know each other better.

758
00:30:55,780 --> 00:30:57,420
(Getting tired of reading)

759
00:30:57,430 --> 00:30:58,520
My eyes are so dry.

760
00:30:58,520 --> 00:30:59,760
I'm taking out my lenses.

761
00:31:00,050 --> 00:31:01,070
Can't see things clearly.

762
00:31:01,070 --> 00:31:02,430
Are these two connected at all?

763
00:31:02,430 --> 00:31:03,420
Probably.

764
00:31:03,420 --> 00:31:04,350
They put them together.

765
00:31:07,230 --> 00:31:08,470
This is so hard to crack.

766
00:31:10,350 --> 00:31:11,590
I'm getting sleepier.

767
00:31:14,280 --> 00:31:16,590
It must be linking letters with numbers.

768
00:31:16,590 --> 00:31:17,520
That's what I thought.

769
00:31:17,520 --> 00:31:18,400
It's not that simple.

770
00:31:18,800 --> 00:31:20,830
We need to guess what it really means.

771
00:31:20,830 --> 00:31:21,710
That's the key.

772
00:31:24,500 --> 00:31:28,820
(Qiong)

773
00:31:33,230 --> 00:31:34,160
Village chief.

774
00:31:38,950 --> 00:31:39,920
Big news.

775
00:31:43,560 --> 00:31:44,760
This is a license plate number.

776
00:31:44,760 --> 00:31:46,940
(Chen Yijia: Puzzle Book 3 points to
a license plate)

777
00:31:46,950 --> 00:31:47,880
Come on, let me see.

778
00:31:48,070 --> 00:31:49,280
We couldn't solve this one.

779
00:31:49,680 --> 00:31:50,760
I figured it out.

780
00:31:50,950 --> 00:31:51,590
You did?

781
00:31:51,590 --> 00:31:52,560
I've cracked this one.

782
00:31:52,950 --> 00:31:53,640
Impressive.

783
00:31:54,800 --> 00:31:57,160
Maybe it's because
I like detective stuff,

784
00:31:57,160 --> 00:31:58,920
like novels, movies, and shows.

785
00:31:58,920 --> 00:32:01,160
When I saw that sheet full of text,

786
00:32:01,160 --> 00:32:02,600
the first two words on it

787
00:32:02,600 --> 00:32:03,950
reminded me of a license plate.

788
00:32:03,950 --> 00:32:04,640
(Qiong)

789
00:32:04,640 --> 00:32:07,310
Every day, I see plates
starting with Qiong,

790
00:32:07,310 --> 00:32:08,710
so it instantly reminded me of one.

791
00:32:08,710 --> 00:32:10,190
(Qiong)

792
00:32:10,190 --> 00:32:12,710
Plus, I'm sensitive to
numbers and letters

793
00:32:12,710 --> 00:32:15,640
than to words themselves.

794
00:32:15,640 --> 00:32:17,400
Even when there's a ton of text,

795
00:32:17,400 --> 00:32:19,280
I just tune it out

796
00:32:19,280 --> 00:32:20,950
and focus on the letters instead.

797
00:32:20,950 --> 00:32:23,310
It's like something glows in your vision.

798
00:32:23,310 --> 00:32:24,710
So I connect them together.

799
00:32:26,710 --> 00:32:28,710
(Qiong ADK9961)
I guessed that's a plate number.

800
00:32:29,070 --> 00:32:31,350
But I couldn't work out the time.

801
00:32:32,280 --> 00:32:33,280
I figured it out already.

802
00:32:37,350 --> 00:32:38,470
Did you get good grades?

803
00:32:39,640 --> 00:32:40,110
Of course.

804
00:32:41,000 --> 00:32:41,980
You can tell you didn't.

805
00:32:45,470 --> 00:32:46,350
I don't like reading

806
00:32:46,350 --> 00:32:47,000
words like these.

807
00:32:47,000 --> 00:32:48,760
I already forget the top part.

808
00:32:49,880 --> 00:32:51,880
I once stayed in nine cities
away from home.

809
00:32:51,880 --> 00:32:52,830
This long journey was

810
00:32:52,830 --> 00:32:54,040
just about collecting...

811
00:32:54,040 --> 00:32:55,710
I don't feel like looking for the card.

812
00:32:57,280 --> 00:32:59,400
Maybe it's because my emotions

813
00:33:00,000 --> 00:33:03,470
and my mind are still stuck
in the previous round.

814
00:33:04,520 --> 00:33:06,190
So honestly, most of the time,

815
00:33:06,190 --> 00:33:08,430
I wasn't even really finishing the game.

816
00:33:08,800 --> 00:33:10,430
I was actually thinking hard

817
00:33:10,920 --> 00:33:13,880
about how we could clear up
the misunderstanding.

818
00:33:26,950 --> 00:33:28,680
It all comes down to time and place?

819
00:33:29,110 --> 00:33:29,800
Just this sheet?

820
00:33:29,800 --> 00:33:30,640
This one.

821
00:33:30,640 --> 00:33:31,280
That's simple.

822
00:33:31,280 --> 00:33:32,100
We'll go with this.

823
00:33:33,590 --> 00:33:34,560
It points to one.

824
00:33:34,560 --> 00:33:37,280
All the travels, all the seasons.

825
00:33:45,040 --> 00:33:45,920
I got it now.

826
00:33:45,920 --> 00:33:47,160
You got it too, right?

827
00:33:47,520 --> 00:33:48,880
I should've known the time.

828
00:33:50,470 --> 00:33:51,560
You know the time?

829
00:33:55,800 --> 00:33:57,820
(Xuan Cheng: the Invitation Card
appears at 13:05)

830
00:33:57,830 --> 00:33:59,950
Because it says,

831
00:34:00,310 --> 00:34:02,040
all the travels and

832
00:34:02,040 --> 00:34:04,000
all the seasons

833
00:34:04,000 --> 00:34:05,310
point to the same destination,

834
00:34:05,310 --> 00:34:05,900
which is one.

835
00:34:05,900 --> 00:34:07,640
(All the travels and the seasons point to 1)

836
00:34:07,640 --> 00:34:09,630
So it means the hour and minute hands

837
00:34:09,630 --> 00:34:11,190
both point at one.

838
00:34:17,150 --> 00:34:18,000
I think

839
00:34:18,000 --> 00:34:19,560
I know what time it means now.

840
00:34:22,600 --> 00:34:23,090
You do?

841
00:34:23,090 --> 00:34:23,870
I know the location.

842
00:34:24,430 --> 00:34:25,470
So, can we team up?

843
00:34:25,470 --> 00:34:26,150
Let's trade info.

844
00:34:26,430 --> 00:34:27,000
Sure.

845
00:34:34,520 --> 00:34:35,910
Wait, I have one condition.

846
00:34:36,800 --> 00:34:38,600
When I'm in danger,
you give me one vote.

847
00:34:39,230 --> 00:34:39,600
Sure.

848
00:34:39,600 --> 00:34:40,120
You promise?

849
00:34:40,120 --> 00:34:40,470
Yes.

850
00:34:40,470 --> 00:34:40,870
Deal.

851
00:34:41,600 --> 00:34:42,670
A license plate.

852
00:34:44,120 --> 00:34:48,390
Qiong ADK9961.

853
00:34:51,670 --> 00:34:53,910
The time is in the afternoon.

854
00:34:53,910 --> 00:34:56,360
1:05 PM.

855
00:34:56,360 --> 00:34:57,280
Or maybe 1:10 PM.

856
00:34:57,280 --> 00:34:59,230
Because it says
everything points to one.

857
00:34:59,230 --> 00:35:01,800
Meaning both hands point at one.

858
00:35:01,800 --> 00:35:02,870
That's how I understand it.

859
00:35:03,840 --> 00:35:05,080
And 1:05 PM

860
00:35:05,080 --> 00:35:06,470
feels like a reasonable time.

861
00:35:06,910 --> 00:35:08,760
Well, that's one way

862
00:35:08,760 --> 00:35:09,560
to look at it.

863
00:35:09,560 --> 00:35:11,390
There's no other clues about time.

864
00:35:11,950 --> 00:35:12,800
If this card...

865
00:35:12,800 --> 00:35:14,080
If you crack the other two books,

866
00:35:14,080 --> 00:35:15,390
just let me and Huang know.

867
00:35:16,390 --> 00:35:17,190
Alright.

868
00:35:18,670 --> 00:35:20,040
The time might not be right.

869
00:35:20,040 --> 00:35:21,800
But I'm sure my location is right.

870
00:35:24,000 --> 00:35:24,630
However,

871
00:35:25,360 --> 00:35:26,030
Xuan Cheng,

872
00:35:26,900 --> 00:35:28,150
maybe it's not afternoon.

873
00:35:28,150 --> 00:35:29,470
(It could be 13:05 or 01:05.)

874
00:35:29,470 --> 00:35:30,320
What time is it now?

875
00:35:31,120 --> 00:35:32,320
It's just past one.

876
00:35:32,320 --> 00:35:33,230
It's one-thirty.

877
00:35:36,430 --> 00:35:37,150
What happened?

878
00:35:37,150 --> 00:35:37,950
Exchanging info?

879
00:35:37,950 --> 00:35:39,000
Let's go check it out.

880
00:35:43,190 --> 00:35:43,600
Where?

881
00:35:43,600 --> 00:35:44,220
Tell me where.

882
00:35:44,430 --> 00:35:44,800
Where?

883
00:35:45,120 --> 00:35:45,630
That plate.

884
00:35:45,630 --> 00:35:47,470
License plate.

885
00:35:49,760 --> 00:35:51,040
We have to go out tomorrow.

886
00:36:00,870 --> 00:36:01,560
Let me go first.

887
00:36:03,150 --> 00:36:04,190
Sir, I'm the first.

888
00:36:07,660 --> 00:36:09,300
(Roadside Parking Area)

889
00:36:09,320 --> 00:36:10,230
You got it?

890
00:36:14,190 --> 00:36:14,910
Didn't see it.

891
00:36:14,910 --> 00:36:15,910
(No Invitation Card)

892
00:36:15,910 --> 00:36:17,630
The time is off.

893
00:36:17,820 --> 00:36:20,260
(Time and place must match
to get the card.)

894
00:36:20,280 --> 00:36:22,120
How did you know to run this way?

895
00:36:22,280 --> 00:36:23,520
Because all the cars are here.

896
00:36:23,950 --> 00:36:25,670
Your brain works pretty well.

897
00:36:25,670 --> 00:36:26,390
Not bad.

898
00:36:27,150 --> 00:36:28,600
Sharp mind.

899
00:36:33,190 --> 00:36:34,150
You found it?

900
00:36:34,150 --> 00:36:34,950
No.

901
00:36:35,360 --> 00:36:36,470
What did it turn out to be?

902
00:36:36,470 --> 00:36:37,360
It's a license plate.

903
00:36:37,910 --> 00:36:38,280
Right.

904
00:36:38,280 --> 00:36:39,520
It's a license plate.

905
00:36:39,520 --> 00:36:40,670
The one with AD something?

906
00:36:41,470 --> 00:36:42,600
You're so smart.

907
00:36:42,840 --> 00:36:43,670
This one's tougher.

908
00:36:43,670 --> 00:36:44,560
This part's about time.

909
00:36:45,000 --> 00:36:46,470
(Puzzle Book 1. Hint: Couple)
Couple?

910
00:36:46,470 --> 00:36:47,470
This is about location.

911
00:36:47,470 --> 00:36:48,120
What about that?

912
00:36:48,120 --> 00:36:49,290
(Location)
It should be time.

913
00:36:49,340 --> 00:36:50,980
(Time)

914
00:36:57,840 --> 00:36:58,630
The hint is couple.

915
00:36:59,420 --> 00:37:16,700
(Hint: couple)

916
00:37:16,710 --> 00:37:17,600
I figured it out.

917
00:37:17,870 --> 00:37:18,910
Huang Jiawei, let's move.

918
00:37:18,910 --> 00:37:19,800
Huang Jiawei.

919
00:37:21,080 --> 00:37:21,870
Swimming pool.

920
00:37:22,390 --> 00:37:23,150
Go, now!

921
00:37:24,840 --> 00:37:25,430
There is

922
00:37:25,430 --> 00:37:26,430
a typical puzzle,

923
00:37:26,430 --> 00:37:28,430
where you need to match couples

924
00:37:28,430 --> 00:37:30,670
sometimes based on their jewelry

925
00:37:30,670 --> 00:37:32,080
or other things they wear,

926
00:37:32,080 --> 00:37:33,600
like details about their looks.

927
00:37:33,600 --> 00:37:34,870
You pair one guy and one girl

928
00:37:34,870 --> 00:37:36,150
and see who matches best.

929
00:37:36,520 --> 00:37:37,670
So when I saw the necklace,

930
00:37:37,670 --> 00:37:40,040
I knew right away they were a couple.

931
00:37:40,040 --> 00:37:41,390
(Couple)

932
00:37:41,390 --> 00:37:42,150
Their name tags.

933
00:37:42,150 --> 00:37:43,560
Si Weiming and Pu'er.

934
00:37:43,560 --> 00:37:44,870
Si Weiming, Pu'er.

935
00:37:44,870 --> 00:37:47,090
I repeated it a few time
and realized

936
00:37:47,090 --> 00:37:48,760
it sounded like swimming pool in English.

937
00:37:49,520 --> 00:37:50,840
(Si Weiming, Pu'er)
The place

938
00:37:50,840 --> 00:37:52,360
where I fell in. So I remember it.

939
00:37:52,360 --> 00:37:53,600
I called Huang Jiawei out.

940
00:37:53,600 --> 00:37:54,520
We ran over right away.

941
00:37:58,470 --> 00:37:59,600
Walk around the pool.

942
00:38:01,280 --> 00:38:02,430
What does it look like?

943
00:38:03,000 --> 00:38:03,910
A single card.

944
00:38:04,300 --> 00:38:05,870
(They cracked the clue.)
Swimming pool.

945
00:38:05,870 --> 00:38:06,600
Hurry.

946
00:38:06,600 --> 00:38:07,320
The swimming pool.

947
00:38:07,320 --> 00:38:08,230
Ah!

948
00:38:08,230 --> 00:38:09,320
I figured it out.

949
00:38:09,840 --> 00:38:10,430
Hurry up.

950
00:38:10,430 --> 00:38:11,120
Someone's coming.

951
00:38:11,360 --> 00:38:12,520
I don't know the time.

952
00:38:15,040 --> 00:38:15,840
I didn't crack

953
00:38:15,840 --> 00:38:16,870
the puzzle about time.

954
00:38:17,060 --> 00:38:19,020
(Match the code to a clock face and swap)

955
00:38:19,020 --> 00:38:20,780
(the hour and minute hands
to get the time.)

956
00:38:26,740 --> 00:38:31,020
(Invitation Card appears at 02:00.)

957
00:38:31,360 --> 00:38:32,870
Shoes off.

958
00:38:35,520 --> 00:38:37,190
We're looking for the card, right?

959
00:38:38,230 --> 00:38:39,760
I want that date chance,

960
00:38:39,760 --> 00:38:41,630
a chance to talk about the answer.

961
00:38:42,280 --> 00:38:43,150
I'm really anxious.

962
00:38:43,520 --> 00:38:44,910
I have to find that card.

963
00:38:44,910 --> 00:38:46,950
I really want the chance for this date.

964
00:38:48,230 --> 00:38:49,710
I want to go on an off-island date.

965
00:38:49,710 --> 00:38:52,000
It could be something new and exciting.

966
00:38:54,630 --> 00:38:56,150
No way it's in there, right?

967
00:38:58,600 --> 00:38:59,840
The rain's getting heavier.

968
00:39:01,320 --> 00:39:02,630
It's pouring so hard.

969
00:39:04,280 --> 00:39:05,230
This rain is crazy.

970
00:39:05,560 --> 00:39:06,800
What should we even do?

971
00:39:17,040 --> 00:39:19,910
It's so hard to find it
in such a huge pool.

972
00:39:21,080 --> 00:39:23,280
I can tell Yan really wants
a date this time.

973
00:39:23,280 --> 00:39:24,710
I have to get that Invitation Card.

974
00:39:25,630 --> 00:39:28,150
Still couldn't find it… I'm losing it.

975
00:39:34,020 --> 00:39:39,220
(Congrats! You've found the Invitation Card.
Invite someone you like for a date.)

976
00:39:51,710 --> 00:39:52,070
I got it.

977
00:39:52,070 --> 00:39:53,280
No need to keep looking.

978
00:39:54,760 --> 00:39:55,670
You found it?

979
00:39:55,670 --> 00:39:57,040
Yes, we can leave now.

980
00:39:58,950 --> 00:39:59,470
You found it?

981
00:39:59,470 --> 00:40:00,230
Yeah.

982
00:40:00,230 --> 00:40:01,230
Really?

983
00:40:01,230 --> 00:40:02,120
Yes.

984
00:40:02,120 --> 00:40:02,910
Where is it?

985
00:40:03,670 --> 00:40:04,800
In my pocket.

986
00:40:04,800 --> 00:40:06,430
Can't let anyone snatch it.

987
00:40:06,630 --> 00:40:07,630
It's glowing.

988
00:40:11,840 --> 00:40:13,910
Finally, I got a date with Yang.

989
00:40:14,080 --> 00:40:15,710
Finally catching up with everyone else.

990
00:40:15,710 --> 00:40:17,000
Seems like it's just me and Yang

991
00:40:17,000 --> 00:40:18,320
haven't gone on a date yet.

992
00:40:18,320 --> 00:40:19,380
I'm looking forward to it.

993
00:40:19,380 --> 00:40:20,150
Because I feel

994
00:40:20,150 --> 00:40:23,760
this date might be the best.

995
00:40:23,760 --> 00:40:25,560
It's a luxury date, after all.

996
00:40:26,150 --> 00:40:27,040
So impressive.

997
00:40:27,040 --> 00:40:28,120
Give me a hug.

998
00:40:28,120 --> 00:40:29,150
I'm really moved.

999
00:40:29,150 --> 00:40:30,390
Honestly, I'm deeply touched.

1000
00:40:30,630 --> 00:40:32,230
I never thought he'd actually find it.

1001
00:40:32,230 --> 00:40:33,080
I'm happy.

1002
00:40:33,080 --> 00:40:35,230
Hooray.

1003
00:40:35,230 --> 00:40:36,150
You're amazing.

1004
00:40:36,220 --> 00:40:37,390
Do you want to wipe your feet?

1005
00:40:37,390 --> 00:40:38,230
It's fine.

1006
00:40:38,600 --> 00:40:39,390
I'm so excited.

1007
00:40:40,280 --> 00:40:41,470
Let's look for the third one.

1008
00:40:41,470 --> 00:40:43,230
But they should've gone to
find it already.

1009
00:40:44,840 --> 00:40:48,710
We fools are still cracking puzzles here.

1010
00:40:52,280 --> 00:40:53,560
Big dummy.

1011
00:40:53,560 --> 00:40:54,520
You too.

1012
00:40:58,840 --> 00:40:59,950
Double dummies.

1013
00:41:03,910 --> 00:41:05,670
Hopefully no one's competing with you

1014
00:41:05,670 --> 00:41:07,040
for this.

1015
00:41:07,040 --> 00:41:08,100
They're aiming at that one.

1016
00:41:08,100 --> 00:41:09,710
And we won't fight you for it either.

1017
00:41:09,710 --> 00:41:10,800
You two are the best.

1018
00:41:10,800 --> 00:41:12,990
The four of us living well
is worth more than anything.

1019
00:41:13,360 --> 00:41:15,080
(Puzzle Book 2)
This one's really tough.

1020
00:41:16,230 --> 00:41:17,670
What's that?

1021
00:41:17,670 --> 00:41:19,670
(Puzzle Book 2)

1022
00:41:21,120 --> 00:41:22,320
Could it be numbers?

1023
00:41:22,320 --> 00:41:24,800
Or maybe like half of a letter?

1024
00:41:27,280 --> 00:41:27,950
That's possible.

1025
00:41:30,000 --> 00:41:31,280
Let's check the other side.

1026
00:41:31,620 --> 00:41:34,340
(Looking at the back of the puzzle)

1027
00:41:36,670 --> 00:41:38,080
It really does look like a letter,

1028
00:41:38,080 --> 00:41:38,760
honestly.

1029
00:41:39,150 --> 00:41:40,430
(English?)
I think it's English.

1030
00:41:40,430 --> 00:41:41,360
English?

1031
00:41:41,360 --> 00:41:41,870
Yeah.

1032
00:41:42,280 --> 00:41:43,910
I think it's an English word.

1033
00:41:45,000 --> 00:41:46,360
This one should be a "B".

1034
00:41:46,360 --> 00:41:49,780
(Xuan Cheng checking the puzzle
from the back)

1035
00:41:55,840 --> 00:41:57,630
I don't get it.

1036
00:41:57,910 --> 00:41:59,760
B.

1037
00:42:00,150 --> 00:42:00,950
O, right?

1038
00:42:00,950 --> 00:42:02,470
(Checking the puzzle from the back)

1039
00:42:02,470 --> 00:42:04,040
B, O, C.

1040
00:42:05,080 --> 00:42:05,630
No,

1041
00:42:05,630 --> 00:42:06,910
it doesn't make sense.

1042
00:42:07,190 --> 00:42:08,470
Check the front side.

1043
00:42:08,820 --> 00:42:12,180
(Back to the front puzzle)

1044
00:42:12,190 --> 00:42:13,230
P, B.

1045
00:42:17,150 --> 00:42:18,190
Something about hotpot?

1046
00:42:18,710 --> 00:42:19,630
That's not right.

1047
00:42:30,950 --> 00:42:32,040
Did you find it?

1048
00:42:32,150 --> 00:42:33,000
They found it.

1049
00:42:36,150 --> 00:42:37,150
I got it.

1050
00:42:37,800 --> 00:42:38,560
Xuan Cheng,

1051
00:42:38,560 --> 00:42:39,390
tell me, please.

1052
00:42:39,390 --> 00:42:40,390
This one is U.

1053
00:42:40,390 --> 00:42:41,710
Pub cup.

1054
00:42:41,710 --> 00:42:43,390
The cup from that pub.

1055
00:42:43,390 --> 00:42:45,060
(Pub)

1056
00:42:45,060 --> 00:42:46,840
(Cup)

1057
00:42:46,840 --> 00:42:47,630
Hurry!

1058
00:42:51,470 --> 00:42:52,560
Huang Jiawei, watch out!

1059
00:43:21,080 --> 00:43:22,230
We've been searching forever.

1060
00:43:22,230 --> 00:43:23,430
But still can't find it.

1061
00:43:24,520 --> 00:43:25,360
It's hard to spot.

1062
00:43:36,800 --> 00:43:37,870
Did you find it?

1063
00:43:37,870 --> 00:43:38,520
No.

1064
00:43:42,080 --> 00:43:42,800
If we fail,

1065
00:43:42,800 --> 00:43:44,320
it'll make us look silly.

1066
00:43:44,800 --> 00:43:45,800
It's not over here?

1067
00:43:46,520 --> 00:43:47,800
Looks like it's not here.

1068
00:43:50,560 --> 00:43:51,870
Could someone else have found it?

1069
00:43:52,910 --> 00:43:53,870
Probably not.

1070
00:43:54,900 --> 00:43:56,660
(The time and place have to match.)

1071
00:43:56,670 --> 00:43:57,630
Nothing yet?

1072
00:43:57,630 --> 00:43:58,870
No, still no luck.

1073
00:44:00,950 --> 00:44:02,950
Attention, islanders.

1074
00:44:02,950 --> 00:44:06,360
The first Invitation Card
has been found by Zhao Enda.

1075
00:44:06,740 --> 00:44:09,180
(Zhao Enda obtained the Invitation Card.)

1076
00:44:09,190 --> 00:44:11,040
Wow, it's really bright.

1077
00:44:12,000 --> 00:44:13,390
It only lights up when you touch it.

1078
00:44:14,040 --> 00:44:15,190
It was dark before.

1079
00:44:16,520 --> 00:44:18,190
Congrats to the rest of the islanders.

1080
00:44:18,190 --> 00:44:20,950
(Puzzle Book 2: Pub)
The other two cards' spots are unlocked.

1081
00:44:21,150 --> 00:44:24,390
But the time puzzles remain unsolved.

1082
00:44:24,520 --> 00:44:25,870
So we have to crack it.

1083
00:44:26,800 --> 00:44:28,040
I'll take care of this tomorrow.

1084
00:44:28,040 --> 00:44:29,870
(Puzzle Book 3: Car)

1085
00:44:29,870 --> 00:44:32,470
Alright.

1086
00:44:32,470 --> 00:44:33,600
Let's head back.

1087
00:44:38,600 --> 00:44:39,490
Grab something to eat,

1088
00:44:39,490 --> 00:44:39,910
Yang?

1089
00:44:42,230 --> 00:44:42,600
Let me.

1090
00:44:42,600 --> 00:44:43,800
That was pretty cool.

1091
00:44:43,800 --> 00:44:44,320
Why?

1092
00:44:44,560 --> 00:44:45,460
Because you found it?

1093
00:44:45,870 --> 00:44:46,360
Exactly.

1094
00:44:46,520 --> 00:44:47,600
I finally found it.

1095
00:44:47,710 --> 00:44:49,280
I've been the only one
without a date.

1096
00:44:49,670 --> 00:44:51,360
Guess it's my turn to go on one.

1097
00:44:52,320 --> 00:44:55,000
And it's even a luxury date.

1098
00:44:56,670 --> 00:44:57,630
Looking forward to it.

1099
00:44:58,080 --> 00:44:58,950
Thank you.

1100
00:45:04,630 --> 00:45:06,000
Finally, I can go out.

1101
00:45:06,760 --> 00:45:07,910
I'll get it tomorrow.

1102
00:45:07,910 --> 00:45:08,710
You can count on me.

1103
00:45:09,670 --> 00:45:11,560
I promise you that.

1104
00:45:11,910 --> 00:45:12,670
How do you get it

1105
00:45:12,670 --> 00:45:13,520
tomorrow?

1106
00:45:14,000 --> 00:45:14,800
I've got a plan.

1107
00:45:15,360 --> 00:45:15,870
You think...

1108
00:45:16,190 --> 00:45:17,840
You think I don't use my brain?

1109
00:45:18,040 --> 00:45:19,840
Don't judge a book by its cover.

1110
00:45:19,840 --> 00:45:21,390
I am careless sometimes,

1111
00:45:21,390 --> 00:45:24,470
but I'm a total hopeless romantic.

1112
00:45:25,000 --> 00:45:26,430
So honestly, I don't know

1113
00:45:26,430 --> 00:45:27,390
why you asked me

1114
00:45:27,390 --> 00:45:28,760
that question today.

1115
00:45:28,760 --> 00:45:30,870
Maybe it's because you think I look like

1116
00:45:30,950 --> 00:45:32,600
the kind of person who often...

1117
00:45:32,600 --> 00:45:33,950
keeps feelings to themselves

1118
00:45:33,950 --> 00:45:35,150
or sometimes does things

1119
00:45:35,150 --> 00:45:36,430
without much attention to detail.

1120
00:45:36,630 --> 00:45:38,150
But honestly, you're always on my mind.

1121
00:45:38,520 --> 00:45:40,190
And I just realized something.

1122
00:45:40,190 --> 00:45:42,000
The best part on this island

1123
00:45:42,000 --> 00:45:43,710
is having you with me.

1124
00:45:43,900 --> 00:45:48,380
(Lu Yanting & Huang Jiawei's Room)

1125
00:45:48,390 --> 00:45:49,670
I'll lock the car tight.

1126
00:45:49,670 --> 00:45:50,190
Anyway,

1127
00:45:50,190 --> 00:45:51,360
it must be inside the car.

1128
00:45:51,360 --> 00:45:53,260
(Xuan Cheng & Zhao Enda's Room)

1129
00:45:57,120 --> 00:45:59,630
One of the puzzle is about the pub.

1130
00:45:59,910 --> 00:46:04,190
We might need to
wait there directly tomorrow.

1131
00:46:13,670 --> 00:46:15,390
What if you can't find it tomorrow?

1132
00:46:16,470 --> 00:46:17,710
Then we'd have nothing to eat.

1133
00:46:18,360 --> 00:46:19,230
Good night.

1134
00:46:21,630 --> 00:46:22,800
I don't feel good.

1135
00:46:23,080 --> 00:46:24,120
Been searching for ages.

1136
00:46:24,870 --> 00:46:25,760
There's still a chance.

1137
00:46:26,560 --> 00:46:27,600
What if we can't find it?

1138
00:46:28,280 --> 00:46:29,040
Then...

1139
00:46:29,040 --> 00:46:30,320
I'll cook for you.

1140
00:46:30,600 --> 00:46:31,520
No lousy meal.

1141
00:46:31,520 --> 00:46:32,360
I'll cook for you.

1142
00:46:33,760 --> 00:46:35,390
Forever yours, Xiaohan.

1143
00:46:36,360 --> 00:46:37,080
Han.

1144
00:46:44,740 --> 00:46:45,900
(Puzzle Book)

1145
00:46:45,900 --> 00:46:51,540
(Who will get
the remaining Invitation Cards?)

1146
00:46:51,940 --> 00:46:55,900
(Day 7)

1147
00:46:58,360 --> 00:46:59,430
Morning.

1148
00:46:59,430 --> 00:47:04,220
(10:30 AM)

1149
00:47:08,300 --> 00:47:11,140
(Two Invitation Cards left)

1150
00:47:21,470 --> 00:47:22,950
I realized

1151
00:47:22,950 --> 00:47:24,950
I might need to make the first move.

1152
00:47:25,360 --> 00:47:27,230
So I got up early

1153
00:47:27,230 --> 00:47:28,350
and became the first one

1154
00:47:28,350 --> 00:47:29,520
to explore the clue.

1155
00:47:38,630 --> 00:47:41,320
I knew the clue was the plate.

1156
00:47:42,120 --> 00:47:43,450
When I reached the parking spot,

1157
00:47:43,450 --> 00:47:44,430
I spotted the car.

1158
00:47:44,430 --> 00:47:46,710
But I still didn't know about the time.

1159
00:48:18,630 --> 00:48:19,870
Open the fuel tank?

1160
00:48:49,000 --> 00:48:50,120
Open the fuel tank.

1161
00:49:25,020 --> 00:49:26,420
(Obtained a phone)

1162
00:49:33,430 --> 00:49:35,190
Back then, I really wasn't sure

1163
00:49:35,190 --> 00:49:36,950
what the Invitation Card
would look like.

1164
00:49:37,280 --> 00:49:38,670
(Tape)
So I did something silly.

1165
00:49:38,670 --> 00:49:40,230
I took every single thing

1166
00:49:40,230 --> 00:49:41,430
from the car out and started

1167
00:49:41,430 --> 00:49:42,430
going through them.

1168
00:49:47,020 --> 00:49:47,860
(Files)

1169
00:49:47,860 --> 00:49:48,860
(Parts)

1170
00:49:51,040 --> 00:49:51,940
I checked everything,

1171
00:49:51,940 --> 00:49:53,630
but I still had no clue.

1172
00:49:53,760 --> 00:49:55,360
So I came up with another idea.

1173
00:49:56,080 --> 00:49:56,870
I decided to wait.

1174
00:49:56,870 --> 00:49:58,320
(There's always a way.)

1175
00:49:58,320 --> 00:50:00,150
I couldn't crack the puzzle about time,

1176
00:50:00,390 --> 00:50:01,470
so I locked the car door

1177
00:50:01,470 --> 00:50:02,120
and sat inside.

1178
00:50:02,120 --> 00:50:04,190
No one's gonna touch these things.

1179
00:50:11,850 --> 00:50:13,760
(10:50 AM)
Anyway, I'll go on a date with Jiayi.

1180
00:50:13,760 --> 00:50:15,300
(11:40 AM)

1181
00:50:21,040 --> 00:50:22,120
You're not going out at all?

1182
00:50:22,120 --> 00:50:22,990
You don't want a date?

1183
00:50:24,120 --> 00:50:25,280
I do, actually.

1184
00:50:30,190 --> 00:50:32,560
I was thinking about talking to Jiayi.

1185
00:50:32,560 --> 00:50:34,190
Because honestly, yesterday…

1186
00:50:34,190 --> 00:50:35,430
During that polygraph session,

1187
00:50:35,430 --> 00:50:36,430
my way of...

1188
00:50:37,800 --> 00:50:38,870
expressing myself…

1189
00:50:38,870 --> 00:50:40,390
and even my understanding…

1190
00:50:40,390 --> 00:50:41,840
were not on the spot.

1191
00:50:42,760 --> 00:50:45,190
(8 AM) So I wanted to make her breakfast

1192
00:50:45,190 --> 00:50:47,740
and explain to her

1193
00:50:47,740 --> 00:50:49,670
what was going through my mind
at the time.

1194
00:50:50,390 --> 00:50:51,670
Because right now, clearing up

1195
00:50:51,670 --> 00:50:53,470
the misunderstanding matters most.

1196
00:50:54,150 --> 00:50:55,480
(Waiting for Liu Jiayi)
Listen,

1197
00:50:55,480 --> 00:50:57,630
don't rush it.

1198
00:50:58,120 --> 00:50:59,000
If you're in a hurry

1199
00:50:59,000 --> 00:51:00,670
to explain something to Jiayi,

1200
00:51:00,670 --> 00:51:01,760
she might get nervous.

1201
00:51:02,360 --> 00:51:04,150
Yesterday, I asked that question

1202
00:51:04,150 --> 00:51:05,000
about our date.

1203
00:51:05,000 --> 00:51:05,870
At that moment, I...

1204
00:51:05,870 --> 00:51:06,800
But in her heart,

1205
00:51:06,800 --> 00:51:07,600
she feel that

1206
00:51:07,600 --> 00:51:09,630
your feelings for her
lean more toward logic.

1207
00:51:10,840 --> 00:51:12,150
If you still want to pursue her,

1208
00:51:12,150 --> 00:51:13,040
show her

1209
00:51:13,040 --> 00:51:15,560
that you genuinely like her,

1210
00:51:15,560 --> 00:51:16,230
not just based on

1211
00:51:16,230 --> 00:51:17,520
a pros-and-cons list

1212
00:51:17,520 --> 00:51:18,990
or whatever she seems suitable.

1213
00:51:18,990 --> 00:51:20,460
Don't treat her well

1214
00:51:20,460 --> 00:51:22,080
only after weighing the pros and cons.

1215
00:51:22,080 --> 00:51:22,520
Right?

1216
00:51:22,520 --> 00:51:23,660
You like her. That's enough.

1217
00:51:23,670 --> 00:51:24,800
You think she wanted you

1218
00:51:24,800 --> 00:51:26,230
to give a more emotional answer?

1219
00:51:26,710 --> 00:51:29,000
No, I didn't understand the question.

1220
00:51:29,600 --> 00:51:31,280
My Chinese really isn't that great.

1221
00:51:31,840 --> 00:51:33,910
But I think you can look at it this way,

1222
00:51:33,910 --> 00:51:35,430
if she actually likes you,

1223
00:51:35,870 --> 00:51:37,910
no matter what you say, she'll like it.

1224
00:51:39,760 --> 00:51:40,840
Don't get too hung up on

1225
00:51:40,840 --> 00:51:41,950
a perfect answer.

1226
00:51:41,950 --> 00:51:43,670
Because if she likes you,

1227
00:51:43,670 --> 00:51:45,630
she won't overthink it.

1228
00:51:45,630 --> 00:51:46,150
Also,

1229
00:51:46,150 --> 00:51:48,040
you really need to stop being so gloomy.

1230
00:51:48,040 --> 00:51:48,760
I'm serious.

1231
00:51:54,080 --> 00:51:55,390
Wow, it's pouring out there.

1232
00:51:57,360 --> 00:51:58,120
That's crazy rain.

1233
00:52:07,040 --> 00:52:07,950
Jiayi's here.

1234
00:52:09,630 --> 00:52:10,600
Hey, sweetheart.

1235
00:52:11,390 --> 00:52:12,630
Anyone in there?

1236
00:52:12,910 --> 00:52:14,320
Yanting and Yijia.

1237
00:52:18,230 --> 00:52:19,670
What's with that face?

1238
00:52:33,080 --> 00:52:34,080
Where are you going?

1239
00:52:34,760 --> 00:52:36,000
Heading back to the dorm?

1240
00:52:36,230 --> 00:52:36,840
Come on.

1241
00:52:36,840 --> 00:52:38,080
I made you breakfast.

1242
00:52:38,080 --> 00:52:39,560
But I've already had one.

1243
00:52:41,230 --> 00:52:42,870
I've had breakfast.

1244
00:52:43,040 --> 00:52:44,870
I spent the whole morning
cooking for you.

1245
00:52:44,870 --> 00:52:46,600
Aren't you coming and having a little?

1246
00:52:58,520 --> 00:53:00,150
I don't know what to do.

1247
00:53:00,280 --> 00:53:01,080
Come on.

1248
00:53:01,870 --> 00:53:02,470
Slow down.

1249
00:53:02,800 --> 00:53:03,670
The rain's pouring.

1250
00:53:08,320 --> 00:53:10,150
I was staying in the dorm

1251
00:53:10,150 --> 00:53:10,840
waiting for you.

1252
00:53:11,470 --> 00:53:13,120
Feels like I've waited a century.

1253
00:53:13,670 --> 00:53:14,710
Well, I was talking to

1254
00:53:14,710 --> 00:53:16,150
Tianyu about...

1255
00:53:16,950 --> 00:53:17,710
cracking the code.

1256
00:53:17,710 --> 00:53:18,870
We were...

1257
00:53:20,220 --> 00:53:21,000
It was frustrating.

1258
00:53:24,760 --> 00:53:26,190
I want to eat this one.

1259
00:53:27,040 --> 00:53:27,840
Is this washed?

1260
00:53:30,020 --> 00:53:31,180
(Yogurt and Fruit Platter)

1261
00:53:31,190 --> 00:53:32,140
I can handle it myself.

1262
00:53:32,760 --> 00:53:34,950
I'll carry my own plate.

1263
00:53:34,950 --> 00:53:35,530
It's fine.

1264
00:53:35,530 --> 00:53:36,430
You got breakfast too?

1265
00:53:36,430 --> 00:53:37,840
Yeah, all thanks to my bestie.

1266
00:53:38,600 --> 00:53:39,670
I'm so happy right now.

1267
00:53:39,670 --> 00:53:40,870
Time to enjoy delicious meal.

1268
00:53:43,120 --> 00:53:44,560
I got it, I can do it myself.

1269
00:53:46,520 --> 00:53:47,950
Thank you.

1270
00:53:47,950 --> 00:53:48,600
Come on then.

1271
00:53:50,120 --> 00:53:51,360
You didn't even come see me,

1272
00:53:51,360 --> 00:53:52,000
my bestie.

1273
00:53:52,000 --> 00:53:52,520
I didn't know

1274
00:53:52,520 --> 00:53:53,390
you came back.

1275
00:53:53,390 --> 00:53:54,390
I waited a century.

1276
00:53:56,560 --> 00:53:57,360
So envious.

1277
00:53:58,360 --> 00:53:59,390
Yijia, want some noodles?

1278
00:53:59,600 --> 00:54:00,840
I'm good.

1279
00:54:04,540 --> 00:54:07,180
(noodles)

1280
00:54:10,800 --> 00:54:11,910
He's cooking noodles.

1281
00:54:11,910 --> 00:54:13,080
Shrimp noodles.

1282
00:54:13,080 --> 00:54:14,080
Smells amazing.

1283
00:54:17,760 --> 00:54:19,080
Thanks for your kindness.

1284
00:54:21,470 --> 00:54:22,950
I should have skipped breakfast.

1285
00:54:25,670 --> 00:54:27,080
Look, he's having boxed meal.

1286
00:54:27,080 --> 00:54:28,080
You're having that?

1287
00:54:28,500 --> 00:54:29,320
I'm fine with this.

1288
00:54:29,320 --> 00:54:30,600
I'm already a bit full.

1289
00:54:31,080 --> 00:54:31,910
Here, you eat this.

1290
00:54:32,390 --> 00:54:33,230
I made it for you.

1291
00:54:33,230 --> 00:54:33,800
Take a bite.

1292
00:54:33,800 --> 00:54:34,390
Alright.

1293
00:54:34,390 --> 00:54:35,360
And the rest is yours.

1294
00:54:36,260 --> 00:54:37,080
(Boxed meal)

1295
00:54:37,080 --> 00:54:38,560
Otherwise, I'd feel bad.

1296
00:54:38,560 --> 00:54:40,080
He sat next to me eating a boxed meal.

1297
00:54:40,080 --> 00:54:40,950
No way.

1298
00:54:40,950 --> 00:54:42,230
Yeah, I'd feel bad too.

1299
00:54:42,390 --> 00:54:43,520
The boxed meal is good.

1300
00:55:04,390 --> 00:55:06,080
I'll head back to my room first.

1301
00:55:06,080 --> 00:55:08,940
(12:19 PM)

1302
00:55:09,320 --> 00:55:10,840
I think you really enjoy code breaking.

1303
00:55:10,840 --> 00:55:11,630
Yeah, I do.

1304
00:55:12,320 --> 00:55:13,320
I like solving puzzles.

1305
00:55:13,320 --> 00:55:13,760
Nice.

1306
00:55:13,760 --> 00:55:14,630
So basically,

1307
00:55:15,760 --> 00:55:16,710
you handle the puzzles.

1308
00:55:16,710 --> 00:55:17,670
and I physical stuff.

1309
00:55:17,950 --> 00:55:18,520
Sounds good.

1310
00:55:19,230 --> 00:55:21,040
Attention, islanders.

1311
00:55:23,430 --> 00:55:26,190
The second Invitation Card appears

1312
00:55:26,190 --> 00:55:27,520
right now.

1313
00:55:27,520 --> 00:55:29,140
(Second Invitation Card revealed)

1314
00:55:32,600 --> 00:55:34,150
Twelve twenty.

1315
00:55:39,760 --> 00:55:43,470
Please state the passcode
for the second card.

1316
00:55:44,360 --> 00:55:45,670
Passcode?

1317
00:55:50,120 --> 00:55:53,840
One three one four.

1318
00:55:55,230 --> 00:55:58,900
Congrats to Xuan Cheng
for getting the Invitation Card.

1319
00:55:58,900 --> 00:56:00,560
(Xuan Cheng received the second card)
Yes!

1320
00:56:00,560 --> 00:56:02,840
Now invite the person you like

1321
00:56:02,840 --> 00:56:04,760
to joining today's off-island date.

1322
00:56:06,020 --> 00:56:07,780
(One hour earlier)

1323
00:56:07,780 --> 00:56:09,520
(Got an important clue — the phone)

1324
00:56:09,520 --> 00:56:10,910
Around eleven o'clock,

1325
00:56:10,910 --> 00:56:12,560
I already had the phone in hand.

1326
00:56:12,670 --> 00:56:14,000
(Congrats!)
At twelve twenty,

1327
00:56:14,000 --> 00:56:16,670
(Passcode: 1314)
I saw a pop-up on the phone

1328
00:56:16,950 --> 00:56:18,430
(Start your date.)
about the date.

1329
00:56:18,430 --> 00:56:21,040
Then there was a code: 1314.

1330
00:56:21,950 --> 00:56:22,800
Bingo.

1331
00:56:27,080 --> 00:56:29,910
I guess that plan actually worked.

1332
00:56:29,910 --> 00:56:32,100
(Waiting by the car for the card)

1333
00:56:36,320 --> 00:56:37,710
Congrats!

1334
00:56:38,120 --> 00:56:39,000
I envy you.

1335
00:56:39,000 --> 00:56:40,430
I wanna go out too.

1336
00:56:45,190 --> 00:56:47,360
You look amazing.

1337
00:56:47,630 --> 00:56:48,670
Congrats!

1338
00:56:49,100 --> 00:56:50,120
I spent the whole morning.

1339
00:56:50,120 --> 00:56:51,600
I almost lost my mind over it.

1340
00:56:51,600 --> 00:56:53,040
I turned that car upside down.

1341
00:56:53,630 --> 00:56:54,800
You're incredible.

1342
00:56:54,800 --> 00:56:55,870
Where did you find it?

1343
00:56:55,870 --> 00:56:58,080
There was a phone next to that car.

1344
00:56:58,080 --> 00:56:59,120
Let's return this first.

1345
00:56:59,520 --> 00:57:02,520
No wonder I couldn't find you
this morning.

1346
00:57:02,520 --> 00:57:04,150
I was actually about to go look for you.

1347
00:57:04,150 --> 00:57:05,560
But when I stepped outside,

1348
00:57:05,560 --> 00:57:06,710
it was pouring rain.

1349
00:57:07,040 --> 00:57:08,230
So I went to the dining room.

1350
00:57:08,230 --> 00:57:09,950
Did you finish your black tea?

1351
00:57:09,950 --> 00:57:10,760
Yeah, I finished it.

1352
00:57:10,760 --> 00:57:11,670
I was so anxious.

1353
00:57:11,670 --> 00:57:13,280
Right after I got the phone,

1354
00:57:13,280 --> 00:57:14,320
I stayed here to wait

1355
00:57:14,320 --> 00:57:15,470
right by this car.

1356
00:57:15,470 --> 00:57:16,190
Yeah.

1357
00:57:16,190 --> 00:57:17,360
Waiting for it to appear?

1358
00:57:17,360 --> 00:57:18,630
When I first reached

1359
00:57:18,630 --> 00:57:19,320
this car,

1360
00:57:19,320 --> 00:57:20,840
I immediately locked the car door.

1361
00:57:20,840 --> 00:57:21,990
No one is allowed to come in.

1362
00:57:23,470 --> 00:57:25,080
I'm inviting you, my lady.

1363
00:57:25,230 --> 00:57:25,950
"My lady"?

1364
00:57:25,950 --> 00:57:28,150
I'm asking you out on a date.

1365
00:57:28,150 --> 00:57:28,520
Sure.

1366
00:57:28,520 --> 00:57:29,000
Would you?

1367
00:57:29,000 --> 00:57:29,910
Yeah, I'd love to.

1368
00:57:33,430 --> 00:57:36,230
They said that.

1369
00:57:39,560 --> 00:57:40,710
You didn't even mention it.

1370
00:57:41,360 --> 00:57:41,950
Of course no.

1371
00:57:41,950 --> 00:57:42,940
I could've gone with you.

1372
00:57:42,940 --> 00:57:45,000
I can't let anyone find out.

1373
00:57:45,120 --> 00:57:45,870
I told you

1374
00:57:45,870 --> 00:57:47,120
I'd get it today no matter what.

1375
00:57:47,120 --> 00:57:50,000
Finally, all my effort paid off.

1376
00:57:50,630 --> 00:57:51,560
Are you happy?

1377
00:57:51,760 --> 00:57:52,560
Yes.

1378
00:57:52,950 --> 00:57:53,760
Back then,

1379
00:57:53,760 --> 00:57:55,870
I was walking down that road with Wan.

1380
00:57:55,870 --> 00:57:57,250
How did you feel when you heard...?

1381
00:57:57,250 --> 00:57:58,360
I was thrilled.

1382
00:58:00,120 --> 00:58:01,040
Super happy.

1383
00:58:01,390 --> 00:58:02,520
I'm gonna take a break.

1384
00:58:02,800 --> 00:58:03,430
I'm exhausted.

1385
00:58:03,430 --> 00:58:04,150
I'll take a rest.

1386
00:58:04,150 --> 00:58:05,080
Then I'll get changed.

1387
00:58:05,710 --> 00:58:06,320
Okay?

1388
00:58:07,600 --> 00:58:08,710
Let me walk you upstairs.

1389
00:58:09,760 --> 00:58:11,120
Oh, so you do remember to walk me.

1390
00:58:11,520 --> 00:58:12,360
So you do know...

1391
00:58:12,360 --> 00:58:13,670
Yeah, sorry about that.

1392
00:58:13,670 --> 00:58:14,670
Okay.

1393
00:58:16,190 --> 00:58:18,230
You only walk me
when I've done something big?

1394
00:58:19,520 --> 00:58:20,320
That's not it.

1395
00:58:22,120 --> 00:58:22,670
Go ahead.

1396
00:58:22,670 --> 00:58:23,470
Go have some fun.

1397
00:58:24,230 --> 00:58:25,000
See you.

1398
00:58:33,470 --> 00:58:34,870
When are you guys heading out?

1399
00:58:34,870 --> 00:58:36,150
No idea.

1400
00:58:36,150 --> 00:58:37,080
I wanna ask

1401
00:58:37,080 --> 00:58:38,120
how you figured it out.

1402
00:58:38,120 --> 00:58:38,910
I have no idea.

1403
00:58:39,390 --> 00:58:40,280
No clue at all.

1404
00:58:46,560 --> 00:58:47,600
Out to have fun again.

1405
00:58:48,230 --> 00:58:49,390
So excited.

1406
00:58:58,910 --> 00:59:00,490
I forgot to add cilantro for you today.

1407
00:59:01,280 --> 00:59:02,280
You even have cilantro?

1408
00:59:03,470 --> 00:59:04,430
You can add it tomorrow.

1409
00:59:05,870 --> 00:59:06,600
Alright.

1410
00:59:07,800 --> 00:59:08,990
Any ideas for tomorrow's meal?

1411
00:59:08,990 --> 00:59:09,770
Why that face?

1412
00:59:11,390 --> 00:59:12,630
Any ideas for tomorrow's meal?

1413
00:59:12,630 --> 00:59:13,230
I'll make it.

1414
00:59:13,560 --> 00:59:14,560
Honestly, everything.

1415
00:59:15,520 --> 00:59:16,670
Then it's up to you.

1416
00:59:17,390 --> 00:59:17,950
Yep.

1417
00:59:19,800 --> 00:59:21,190
Then get ready for a surprise.

1418
00:59:32,150 --> 00:59:33,190
Is this yours?

1419
00:59:33,840 --> 00:59:34,080
Yeah.

1420
00:59:34,080 --> 00:59:35,230
Mind if I drink it?

1421
00:59:35,230 --> 00:59:35,950
Go on, take a sip.

1422
00:59:35,950 --> 00:59:36,470
Alright.

1423
00:59:37,710 --> 00:59:38,520
Perfect.

1424
00:59:39,630 --> 00:59:41,520
(15 mins earlier)
Did you finish that black tea?

1425
00:59:41,520 --> 00:59:42,230
Yeah.

1426
00:59:42,230 --> 00:59:42,800
Good.

1427
00:59:43,700 --> 00:59:49,620
(Xuan Cheng's Tea)

1428
00:59:49,630 --> 00:59:51,760
Attention, islanders.

1429
00:59:51,760 --> 00:59:54,490
(Third Invitation Card. 12:45 PM)
The third card is coming soon.

1430
00:59:55,080 --> 00:59:56,430
Only one Date Card left.

1431
00:59:57,000 --> 00:59:58,800
I'm searching everywhere for it.

1432
00:59:58,800 --> 01:00:00,000
Turning this place upside down.

1433
01:00:00,430 --> 01:00:02,150
I really want to go out with him.

1434
01:00:02,150 --> 01:00:02,950
An off-island date.

1435
01:00:03,360 --> 01:00:03,710
Please

1436
01:00:03,710 --> 01:00:05,280
don't wear yourselves out.

1437
01:00:05,280 --> 01:00:05,800
Just wait.

1438
01:00:06,320 --> 01:00:07,670
The clue is already in our hands.

1439
01:00:08,530 --> 01:00:09,840
I want to know what he's thinking.

1440
01:00:09,840 --> 01:00:11,800
That's why I tried my best back then.

1441
01:00:11,800 --> 01:00:13,520
Did any of you guess the time right?

1442
01:00:16,060 --> 01:00:22,940
(Who will get the last Invitation Card?)

1443
01:00:22,940 --> 01:00:39,900
("Live and Love" Release Schedule)

1444
01:00:39,900 --> 01:00:41,630
(Next Episode Preview)

1445
01:00:41,630 --> 01:00:42,470
I've got a feeling.

1446
01:00:42,470 --> 01:00:43,460
If I cannot be with you,

1447
01:00:43,460 --> 01:00:45,120
I'll miss you like crazy.

1448
01:00:45,120 --> 01:00:46,190
Completely crazy.

1449
01:00:46,800 --> 01:00:49,150
But you make me feel kind of unsafe.

1450
01:00:49,430 --> 01:00:50,320
What?

1451
01:00:51,080 --> 01:00:53,080
You mean you think
we're not a good match

1452
01:00:53,280 --> 01:00:55,040
and you and he are better together?

1453
01:00:57,560 --> 01:01:01,000
(Dating History; Personal Info & Spending)
Tonight, the Dark Night Forest opens.

1454
01:01:01,000 --> 01:01:03,600
The Dark Night Forest on the island

1455
01:01:03,600 --> 01:01:06,280
