1456
01:01:06,280 --> 01:01:08,800
What do you mean by
"different paths of growth"?

1457
01:01:08,800 --> 01:01:10,390
How could you check my dating history?

1458
01:01:10,390 --> 01:01:11,870
I'm so mad I could scream.

1459
01:01:12,760 --> 01:01:13,500
Now I regret it.

1460
01:01:13,500 --> 01:01:14,360
(Every Wed at 12 PM)

1461
01:01:14,360 --> 01:01:15,400
(Pursue Love on Balance Island)
Trust me.

1462
01:01:15,420 --> 01:01:15,800
I trust you.

1463
01:01:16,360 --> 01:01:17,430
You're good at this game.

1464
01:01:17,430 --> 01:01:18,000
But I am not.

1465
01:01:18,320 --> 01:01:19,520
I have the intelligence

1466
01:01:19,520 --> 01:01:20,560
and you have the brawn.

1467
01:01:21,190 --> 01:01:21,910
A perfect team.

1468
01:01:22,520 --> 01:01:24,040
I've never been to the seaside before.

1469
01:01:24,360 --> 01:01:25,760
This feels amazing.

1470
01:01:25,760 --> 01:01:27,080
Even my mood's lifted.

1471
01:01:27,080 --> 01:01:27,870
Yeah.

1472
01:01:27,870 --> 01:01:29,360
The puzzle we had earlier.

1473
01:01:29,360 --> 01:01:30,560
The drawing was such a mess.

1474
01:01:32,000 --> 01:01:33,670
I've never been on such a formal date.

1475
01:01:33,670 --> 01:01:35,230
Me neither.

1476
01:01:36,190 --> 01:01:37,360
I got a nickname, Bai.

1477
01:01:37,360 --> 01:01:38,350
Because your skin's fair.

1478
01:01:38,850 --> 01:01:39,990
(Bai)
I'll put it on my bag.

1479
01:01:40,280 --> 01:01:41,380
It'll make me think of you.

1480
01:01:43,000 --> 01:01:44,080
What if

1481
01:01:44,080 --> 01:01:45,390
