1482
01:01:45,390 --> 01:01:46,280
I can't accept that.

1483
01:01:46,280 --> 01:01:47,430
Then why aren't we together?

1484
01:01:49,390 --> 01:01:51,390
(Every Thu. at noon)
Hi, I'm actor Wang Kaimu.

1485
01:01:51,390 --> 01:01:52,800
(Watch Live and Love with us.)
I'm actress Wang Gege.

1486
01:01:52,800 --> 01:01:55,190
(Excited)
This is my first time shipping others.

1487
01:01:55,190 --> 01:01:56,950
Can't wait to see "Live and Love".

1488
01:01:57,520 --> 01:01:58,420
He's secretly pleased.

1489
01:01:58,420 --> 01:01:59,470
He secretly enjoyed that.

1490
01:01:59,470 --> 01:02:01,000
I take back what I just said.

1491
01:02:01,000 --> 01:02:02,230
(Message withdrawn)
Seems

1492
01:02:02,230 --> 01:02:03,040
she's...

1493
01:02:03,040 --> 01:02:04,000
Handsome and gorgeous.

1494
01:02:04,000 --> 01:02:05,470
(Can't help it)
They're a good match.

1495
01:02:05,470 --> 01:02:07,360
You really can't remember Huang Jiawei?

1496
01:02:08,230 --> 01:02:10,470
(Bringing up the wrong topic)
Focus on shipping others.

1497
01:02:10,950 --> 01:02:13,280
(Hold up)
Why does it feel like I'm watching a drama?

1498
01:02:13,340 --> 01:02:14,820
(Brilliant!)

1499
01:02:14,910 --> 01:02:16,800
(They treated the village chief like an NPC)
He's part of their game.

1500
01:02:17,150 --> 01:02:19,120
He intentionally opened it
in front of Jiawei.

1501
01:02:19,120 --> 01:02:19,450
They are

1502
01:02:19,450 --> 01:02:20,800
(Is this okay?)
right next to him.

1503
01:02:20,800 --> 01:02:22,220
Stop it, or he's gonna cry.

1504
01:02:22,220 --> 01:02:22,900
(I'm fine)

1505
01:02:22,950 --> 01:02:24,870
I can't wait to see what happens next.

1506
01:02:24,870 --> 01:02:26,190
(So anxious)
Fidgeting nonstop.

1507
01:02:26,190 --> 01:02:28,470
I really hope someone
will break them apart.
